<number id="E70524C89910FFAA05C749C6AA8387D5" box="[697,705,2001,2015]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" value="2.0">2</number>
+ 
<number id="E70524C89910FFAA05B449C6AA9387D5" box="[714,721,2001,2015]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" value="3.0">3</number>
linear but tip rather abruptly curved anteriorly to join C ~ 
